A customer needs a storage solution for archiving his CCTV (closed circuit television)
workload.
What is the best cost performance optimized solution?
A. IBM Storwize V3700 with SSD only
B. IBM Storwize V3700 with 10K rpm drives and SSD
C. IBM Storwize V3700 with 15Krpm drives
D. IBM Storwize V3700 with turbo feature and NL-SaS drives
Answer: B

about 8TB of Tier 0 Storage. The customer is also planning to add 10 TB of space with
Storwize V7000.
What is the best option of adding the Tier 0 space?
A. Add SSDs to the Storwize V7000 configuration.
B. Externally visualize a Flash System 820 with the Storwize V7000
C. Add an additional Storwize V7000 with SSDs and cluster together.
D. Externally virtualize a Storwize V3700 with SSDs included in the system
Answer: A
